{"tid":1580584,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"施真高：文迪復出強心針","createTime":"2019-09-19T06:52:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-19T07:54:00.000Z","uid":50745,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"004dc81d868473247f07304dd09339984c0ba333","tid":1580584,"uid":50745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T06:52:10.000Z","msg":"【Now Sports-體育】周三歐聯分組賽，英超冠軍曼城作客薩克達，左閘施真高揚言賓祖文文迪復出是強心針。<br />\n自今年5月受傷缺陣，25歲法國後衛賓祖文文迪（Benjamin Mendy）終於傷癒般出，與簡些路等列入歐聯大軍名單，周三有望對薩克達時披甲。「很高興看見他回歸，他養傷期間非常努力，我們需要他。」雖然是競爭對手，烏克蘭國腳施真高也替文迪回歸拍爛手掌，畢竟拉樸迪重創半年，加上史東斯加入十字軍名單，防線兵源告急。 上場英超不敵諾域治，領隊哥迪奧拿在大戰薩克達前夕證實：「史東斯要養傷4至5周。」 屋漏偏逢連夜雨，短期內中場費蘭甸奴或右閘卡爾獲加也有機會客串中堅，「對球隊和領隊而言，這也是一大挑戰。」 薩克達VS曼城 Now TV 644台18/09 03:00直播 Now E 同步直播"},{"pid":"52502687bf2ce7f2a925204ef796b300c1c3124e","tid":1580584,"uid":117906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T06:52:29.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">[公海 文宣 行動整合] 9.29全球抗赤納粹集會<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1579667\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1579667</a><br />\n全世界一齊對準ChiNazi極權！</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BZiskWr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBZiskWr.png&h=b85bf973&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">9.29 Global AntiChiNazi 文宣、資訊、行動整合Channel</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/AntiChinazi929\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FAntiChinazi929&d=gqDWnnaI%2FM4dwC7GJUFj5SWRWsFhQrZK9M853DAdSZ8%3D&h=9b5b2c23\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/AntiChinazi929</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>9.29 Global AntiChiNazi 公海</strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/NfHvOU5TXSG9DxQIRNkxLQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FNfHvOU5TXSG9DxQIRNkxLQ&d=gqDWnnaI%2FM4dwC7GJUFj5SWRWsFhQrZK9M853DAdSZ8%3D&h=ae8f6145\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/